They escaped inspection in Álava in a van with two thousand kilograms of hashish
Five in ten minutes.
Ertzaintza road inspection in the municipality of Armiñón (Álava).
Officers stop two people driving in a van and they run away.
The load, more than two tons of hashish, is unstoppable.
