Actress Heather Locklear arrested for driving under the influence of drugs
Actress Heather Locklear, popular Amanda from Melrose Place, was arrested this weekend in Santa Barbara (California) for driving under the influence of drugs.
A witness saw her make unusual maneuvers as she tried to pull out of a parking lot in Montecito, a spokesperson for the California Highway Patrol told People magazine.
