A witness, who did not appear to recognize the actress at first, saw Locklear moments later pull over on a nearby freeway and get out of her vehicle.
That person also called emergency services because she &quot;feared for Locklear&#39;s life.&quot;
When a police patrol arrived at the scene, they found the actress inside a vehicle that partially blocked the road.
She &quot;appeared disoriented,&quot; so officers took her to a specialized drug and alcohol center for testing.
According to a police spokesperson, the actress cooperated and an excessive amount of alcohol was immediately ruled out, however &quot;we believe that Locklear was under the influence of some medication, which was apparent to the officers at first glance&quot;.
Locklear was arrested on suspicion of driving under the influence of an unspecified substance and was taken into custody around 7pm, although she was released a few hours later.
